{"tid":200420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保良局終跪低！與承辦商解約停辦訓練營","createTime":"2017-04-14T02:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T08:32:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67f360150aca3c26f6a4f212d4a6a70f240f9756","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170414/large/1492133193_f245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170414%2Flarge%2F1492133193_f245.jpg&h=be34d99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保良局領袖紀律訓練營涉虐待學生醜聞早前陸續曝光，事件再有新進展，保良局發聲明，宣佈與承辦機構「導航訓練中心」達成協議決定解約，目前已沒有舉辦任何領袖紀律訓練營活動，並將進行3個月全面檢視。<br />\n<br />\n保良局發聲明交代「領袖紀律訓練營最新安排」，指訓練營目的是以不同活動讓學員提升學術以外領域的領袖才能，該局訓練營專責顧問委員會對該服務正 進行3個月的全面檢視，並與原服務承辦機構「導航訓練中心」達成協議，解除合約。據悉委員會初步認為，日後舉辦同類活動須與時並進，不應再側重於紀律訓練，以照顧不同學校與學生個別差異。而具體活動內容須作何調整，仍有待委員會完成最終報告，提交董事會討論後才能敲定，但可肯定的屆時將會是全新安排。<br />\n<br />\n「保良局領袖紀律訓練營」並非由保良局營辦，而是外判給「導航訓練中心」。該營項目總監、導航訓練中心負責人盧錦昌早前稱，中心2006年起成為保良局外判承辦商，估計導航中心提供的訓練營，佔全港同類訓練課程約70%，每年入營的學員高達2萬人，而保良局屬校學生只佔當中3成。盧又稱，每3年跟保良局續約，現有合約至明年屆滿。"},{"pid":"6f903382ad75dbd7fe9075c087695f2b7e995908","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170414&amp;guid=56562831&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170414%26guid%3D56562831%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=666abf42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170414%26guid%3D56562831%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=28760cc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170414&amp;guid=56562831&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"07cd38e1d7baef4a078a62b5f366315b3c3a5f8d","tid":200420,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b31b1975c879b5acb9781db6cd6d6c6af003f3","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bb0dbf708ee547ae6e5fe7634cbcf66134ab3a","tid":200420,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"停左啫<br />\n咁中左伏班學生點補償？"},{"pid":"2c6437ce50e746cc447ff8d19cf42845950c1e32","tid":200420,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"睇死過左風頭又黎㗎啦"},{"pid":"78af464be18d2aa629a3afbe9edc4c466cc01bab","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62018c299a522c4d81005b9ceef3def2e73bc10e","tid":200420,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"咁快收夠錢停手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b101252df7d657bc73f8619ca1a5721f5937e2f1","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da9c07e381487a31d3eb0a4c7fc5f3d25401c29","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198540fc2b4b3eab301eece9b0ee8ec910c517b7","tid":200420,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e